---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Artikel & Tutorial DeepSeek Malaysia
description: Layari tutorial log masuk DeepSeek, API, prompt, penyelesaian ralat, dan pemasangan Ollama dalam Bahasa Melayu.
eleventyComputed:
  noindex: "{{ pagination.pageNumber > 0 }}"
pagination:
  data: collections.indexablePosts
  size: 10
  alias: posts
  reverse: true
permalink: "posts/{% if pagination.pageNumber > 0 %}page-{{ pagination.pageNumber + 1 }}/{% endif %}index.html"
---

<div class="container" style="padding-top: 60px;">
  <h1 style="font-size: 32px; color: var(--bg-dark); margin-bottom: 20px; border-left: 6px solid var(--primary); padding-left: 20px;">
    Tutorial Teras DeepSeek Malaysia
  </h1>
  <p style="color:#64748b; margin-bottom:40px;">Senarai tutorial keutamaan yang boleh diikuti terus. Laman ini juga ada artikel rujukan auto-jana (lalai noindex, tidak masuk carian Google).</p>

  <div class="posts-list">
    {% for post in posts %}
      <article class="posts-list-item">
        {% if post.data.coverImage %}
        <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="posts-list-thumb">
          <img src="{{ post.data.coverImage | assetUrl }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }}" width="240" height="135" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
        </a>
        {% endif %}
        <div class="posts-list-body">
          <div style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 10px;">{{ post.date | dateFilter }}</div>
          <h2 style="margin:0 0 15px 0; font-size: 24px;"><a href="{{ post.url }}" style="text-decoration:none; color: var(--bg-dark);">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
          <p style="color:#64748b; font-size:15px; margin-bottom:15px;">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
          <a href="{{ post.url }}" style="color:var(--primary); text-decoration:none; font-weight:600; font-size:14px;">Baca artikel &raquo;</a>
        </div>
      </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

  {% if pagination.pages.length > 1 %}
  <nav style="display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 10px; margin: 60px 0;">
    {% for pageEntry in pagination.pages %}
      <a href="{{ pagination.hrefs[loop.index0] }}" style="padding: 10px 18px; border: 1px solid var(--border); text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; {{ 'background: var(--bg-dark); color:#fff; border-color: var(--bg-dark);' if page.url == pagination.hrefs[loop.index0] else 'color:var(--text-main);' }}">
        {{ loop.index }}
      </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </nav>
  {% endif %}
</div>
